Text: "Well. everything start now,when I am thinking about the magic and fantastic\
  \ thing could happen to me, travel aroud a country and meet person and know about\
  \ a new culture it's amazing,and I have been dreaming for long years \n\n      \
  \     And where the travel begins ? well to me this started in 2012 when I decide\
  \ study english for myself and \nthe long and winding road started,and It has been\
  \ hard but the dream don't let it die.And the kid grow up with the same dream and\
  \ still thinking about a one opportunity ,but the last thing that him expected is\
  \ don't make your dream come true .it just the frist lines of a story that will\
  \ come true and just need wait it happen and just depend of the world to him go\
  \ . \n\nAnd he finish this little text saying agiain,the story start in Argentina\
  \ ? It's what we'll know"
